WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.458
Hail Jesus and Mary, dear subscribers of the YouTube channel of the Association "Croatia for Life".

00:00:05.458 --> 00:00:10.615
In this third video, you will meet a special and beautiful young lady,

00:00:10.615 --> 00:00:13.933
whom the Lord has reserved only for pregnant women.

00:00:13.933 --> 00:00:16.136
It is our Dijana Brozović.

00:00:16.136 --> 00:00:20.449
Dijana is the manager of the Center for Life in the city of Zagreb, 

00:00:20.449 --> 00:00:24.111
as well as the manager of the "You are not alone" team for pregnant women.

00:00:24.111 --> 00:00:29.384
’You are not alone'’ are four words that have saved the greatest number of lives so far

00:00:29.384 --> 00:00:32.326
through the activities of our Association "Croatia for Life".

00:00:32.326 --> 00:00:33.560
Let’s meet Dijana.

00:00:44.891 --> 00:00:47.516
Hail Jesus and Mary! My name is Dijana Brozović

00:00:47.516 --> 00:00:53.721
and I am the head of the team for pregnant women "You are not alone" which operates within the Association "Croatia for Life".

00:00:53.721 --> 00:00:58.034
I am also the coordinator of Centers for Life in Croatia.

00:00:58.034 --> 00:01:01.444
We currently have six open Centers for Life –

00:01:01.444 --> 00:01:09.885
in the city of Zagreb, in Zadar, in Split, in Slavonski Brod, in Vinkovci, and here is the newest one opened in Križevci.

00:01:09.885 --> 00:01:15.601
We are currently in one of the Centers for Life, the one in the city of Zagreb,

00:01:15.601 --> 00:01:19.089
which is also the first Center for Life that was opened.

00:01:19.089 --> 00:01:26.390
These very spaces are the spaces where we receive our mothers and pregnant women who are thinking about abortion

00:01:26.390 --> 00:01:31.038
and families who need any kind of help.

00:01:31.038 --> 00:01:38.018
So, in this space we will also present our program: Team for pregnant women "You are not alone".

00:01:38.018 --> 00:01:46.466
The team for pregnant women has been operating since 2014, when our Association was launched in Croatia.

00:01:46.466 --> 00:01:52.042
Somehow, when we started the "40 Days for Life" initiative and our vigils in front of hospitals,

00:01:52.042 --> 00:02:02.669
we realized that we needed something to offer pregnant women and mothers who contact us,

00:02:02.669 --> 00:02:08.316
who are thinking about abortion, so we started this Team for pregnant women.

00:02:08.316 --> 00:02:12.391
You may have noticed that the Team for pregnant women is called ''You are not alone''

00:02:12.391 --> 00:02:18.102
because those four words have saved the greatest number of lives.

00:02:22.428 --> 00:02:25.790
I would like to support this statement with an example.

00:02:25.790 --> 00:02:32.899
Namely, a few months ago we received a call from a lady whose neighbor was pregnant

00:02:32.899 --> 00:02:37.989
and who had an appointment for an abortion the next day.

00:02:37.989 --> 00:02:41.242
So she contacted us for help.

00:02:41.242 --> 00:02:49.514
I gave her my contact number, she gave me her neighbor’s and that girl who was pregnant called me

00:02:49.514 --> 00:02:53.595
literally five minutes before the appointment for the abortion.

00:02:53.595 --> 00:02:59.159
And in those five minutes, I managed to tell her that she won’t be alone, that we will be by her side,

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:06.681
that we will help her in all the ways she needs, and she thanked me and went to her appointment.

00:03:06.681 --> 00:03:14.241
However, after a couple of hours she called me and said that it was this support, that help,

00:03:14.241 --> 00:03:23.046
and the four words ''you are not alone'' that were her greatest support and the reason why she decided to keep her child.

00:03:23.046 --> 00:03:31.705
Because in those words she felt that we were really ready to help her and she felt our sincerity and trust.

00:03:31.705 --> 00:03:35.606
So she decided to keep her child.

00:03:43.029 --> 00:03:51.037
This is just one example of how these four words save lives, and there are many.

00:03:51.037 --> 00:04:00.402
Often today in society we can hear ''the right to choose'', and it is already becoming like a platitude,

00:04:00.402 --> 00:04:06.896
but those women who find themselves in difficult life situations,

00:04:06.896 --> 00:04:11.166
unfortunately have no choice but to have an abortion.

00:04:11.166 --> 00:04:18.125
If their families and the environment turn their backs on them, and everyone is in favor of them having an abortion,

00:04:18.125 --> 00:04:24.740
if they themselves do not have enough opportunities, whether economic or otherwise,

00:04:24.740 --> 00:04:29.383
abortion is often left as their only choice.

00:04:29.383 --> 00:04:33.502
We want to offer them the option that they can keep their child,

00:04:33.502 --> 00:04:38.100
and that they can live and raise their child with dignity.

00:04:42.197 --> 00:04:47.011
Through the team for pregnant women, we help them in different ways:

00:04:47.011 --> 00:04:55.604
by paying rent and utilities, we also help them with gift vouchers for food, hygiene items,

00:04:55.604 --> 00:05:01.790
everything they need for a child, from cribs, strollers, clothes, wet wipes,

00:05:01.790 --> 00:05:08.272
everything they need for their child they can receive here at the Center for Life.

00:05:08.272 --> 00:05:17.048
It means a lot to them. This support is one of the most important support we provide them with.

00:05:17.048 --> 00:05:20.936
However, this is not the only form of help we provide them with.

00:05:20.936 --> 00:05:27.815
We are there for them in all other ways, be it spiritually, morally, psychologically,

00:05:27.815 --> 00:05:31.597
in whatever way they need, that’s how we approach them.

00:05:31.597 --> 00:05:38.119
Namely, the first time they come to us for an interview, they often come exactly to this space,

00:05:38.119 --> 00:05:46.419
and at that first interview we look at the reasons why a woman decides to have an abortion

00:05:46.419 --> 00:05:50.664
and accordingly create the further help she needs.

00:05:50.664 --> 00:05:56.067
We also have a whole range of experts who are at our disposal for any need,

00:05:56.067 --> 00:06:02.585
from gynecologists, lawyers, social workers, psychologists, pediatricians,

00:06:02.585 --> 00:06:08.747
really people of different professions and vocations offer us their help

00:06:08.747 --> 00:06:16.630
and want to be there for those pregnant women and mothers who are in difficult life situations.

00:06:21.890 --> 00:06:25.589
However, this is not the only form of help we provide them.

00:06:25.589 --> 00:06:32.537
Our goal is not to make mothers dependent either on our support and help or on anyone else’s.

00:06:32.537 --> 00:06:41.104
Our goal is for these mothers to become independent, to be able to live independently and raise their children.

00:06:41.104 --> 00:06:50.884
So we encourage mothers to go to school, whether they complete some kind of course or night school,

00:06:50.884 --> 00:06:56.048
anything that will help them get a job later.

00:06:56.048 --> 00:07:04.355
We are also proud of the fact that several of our mothers managed to finish university with their child.

00:07:04.355 --> 00:07:14.550
So I kind of like to say that mothers can really do much more than they think,

00:07:14.550 --> 00:07:21.107
and I even believe that mothers have some kind of supernatural strength

00:07:21.107 --> 00:07:27.950
that is given to them through their child as a motivation to fight even harder,

00:07:27.950 --> 00:07:33.235
to persevere even more and not to give up in life.

00:07:33.235 --> 00:07:41.763
As an example, we have a mother who was in a very difficult life situation.

00:07:41.763 --> 00:07:48.079
At the moment when she became pregnant, she did not see any meaning in her life.

00:07:48.079 --> 00:07:56.476
However, the child really came to her at the right moment and the child somehow saved her life.

00:07:56.476 --> 00:08:04.203
She was forced to have an abortion by her family, but she wanted to give birth to that child

00:08:04.203 --> 00:08:08.951
because she saw the meaning of her life in that child.

00:08:08.951 --> 00:08:16.921
She refused to have an abortion, she kept her child, and she is a mother who finished high school while pregnant,

00:08:16.921 --> 00:08:26.010
and later graduated from high school, enrolled in college and worked alongside her child and graduated from college.

00:08:26.010 --> 00:08:30.768
So there’s nothing a mother can’t do.

00:08:30.768 --> 00:08:38.116
And I believe that every mother who decides to keep her child really has strength,

00:08:38.116 --> 00:08:46.320
because that strength comes from that one new life that she gave to her child.

00:08:53.005 --> 00:08:57.856
We are currently helping 56 families in Croatia.

00:08:57.856 --> 00:09:00.606
However, this figure changes from day to day.

00:09:00.606 --> 00:09:06.155
Every day we receive new families, new families contact us for help.

00:09:06.155 --> 00:09:17.048
Unfortunately, there is currently a difficult financial situation in our country, so it is increasingly difficult to raise children.

00:09:17.048 --> 00:09:25.724
Finances are a growing problem for families to decide to have another child,

00:09:25.724 --> 00:09:37.397
so through our work, mothers still decide to keep the child and that number out of those 56 of families changes every day,

00:09:37.397 --> 00:09:42.799
because some families have become independent and do not need our material help so much anymore.

00:09:42.799 --> 00:09:50.523
And new families are coming. However, all those families still stay here with us.

00:09:50.523 --> 00:09:55.359
We like to say that we act as one big family.

00:09:55.359 --> 00:10:03.367
All these families that we helped when we first started with the Association and with the initiative,

00:10:03.367 --> 00:10:07.770
they are still there with us, we are still in contact, we still hear from each other

00:10:07.770 --> 00:10:15.813
and they know that at any time they need help, they can still count on us,

00:10:15.813 --> 00:10:21.365
they can ask us, they can contact us, so here we really are one big family

00:10:21.365 --> 00:10:27.401
that now counts more than 160 families.

00:10:27.401 --> 00:10:40.899
Namely, 160 lives have been saved since the start of the initiative, so that number is getting bigger and bigger.

00:10:48.813 --> 00:10:57.950
Finally, I would like to tell you another testimony of a mother who met the volunteers in front of the hospital,

00:10:57.950 --> 00:11:00.013
and she was a high school student at the time.

00:11:00.013 --> 00:11:06.233
Namely, when she saw the volunteers, she threw very ugly words at them and thought

00:11:06.233 --> 00:11:12.109
that these people mistreat women, that they are not good, that they discriminate.

00:11:12.109 --> 00:11:18.117
However, three years after that meeting, she became pregnant.

00:11:18.117 --> 00:11:23.556
She made an appointment for an abortion and decided to abort her child,

00:11:23.556 --> 00:11:28.833
due to the fact that she did not have the support of her relatives or her partner.

00:11:28.833 --> 00:11:36.156
However, she remembered those volunteers whom she insulted in front of the hospital and decided to contact us.

00:11:36.156 --> 00:11:44.209
She came to the Center for Life with us, to see what exactly we will tell her, how we will approach her.

00:11:44.209 --> 00:11:53.512
She expected that we would approach her with some kind of condemnation, that we would condemn her for what she wanted to do,

00:11:53.512 --> 00:12:00.435
that we would be the ones to give some kind of monologue and that she would just listen.

00:12:00.435 --> 00:12:06.650
However, she was surprised when she came to the Center for Life that she got her first hug,

00:12:06.650 --> 00:12:14.120
and that for the first time someone honestly asked her how she was doing and what was going on in her life.

00:12:14.120 --> 00:12:23.367
She was surprised that she already felt that trust at that first meeting and told us her whole life story.

00:12:23.367 --> 00:12:31.559
Everything she went through in her childhood, all the difficulties she had to deal with,

00:12:31.559 --> 00:12:38.508
and she was surprised by the fact that this was a part of her life that she had never told anyone,

00:12:38.508 --> 00:12:42.108
and here she told us already at the first meeting.

00:12:42.108 --> 00:12:49.469
The next day we went to see a gynecologist and she heard her child’s heartbeat

00:12:49.469 --> 00:12:57.869
and that was the moment when she decided to keep her child, to accept our help, our support.

00:12:57.869 --> 00:13:03.460
As we were leaving that examination, she asked me why we were doing this,

00:13:03.460 --> 00:13:07.196
why we were there for her, and we didn’t know her at all.

00:13:07.196 --> 00:13:11.565
Why do we care so much about her and her child.

00:13:11.565 --> 00:13:20.477
And the love we gave her surprised her and somehow melted her heart

00:13:20.477 --> 00:13:24.202
and she decided to give her child a chance.

00:13:24.202 --> 00:13:32.392
This is one example, and we could tell you many such life stories.

00:13:39.238 --> 00:13:45.045
I want to thank you all for your prayer support, for your financial support,

00:13:45.045 --> 00:13:51.967
because without your prayer and financial support, we would not be able to act in this way,

00:13:51.967 --> 00:13:56.925
we would not be able to provide these mothers with all that we provide them,

00:13:56.925 --> 00:14:04.792
all this support they need and I thank you from the bottom of my heart on behalf of all mothers,

00:14:04.792 --> 00:14:07.176
on behalf of all rescued children.

00:14:07.176 --> 00:14:11.528
And they are really grateful to you for everything you do for them.

00:14:11.528 --> 00:14:14.027
Your little is really a lot for someone.

00:14:14.027 --> 00:14:20.114
Maybe your five minutes of prayer in front of hospitals can really save someone’s life.

00:14:20.114 --> 00:14:26.274
Your little money that you set aside for the Association means a lot to someone.

00:14:26.274 --> 00:14:29.733
Thank you from the bottom of my heart and I wish you God’s blessing.

00:14:40.779 --> 00:14:46.344
In this video, you got to know our Dijana and the work of the Center for Life in the city of Zagreb.

00:14:46.344 --> 00:14:49.662
We have several Centers for Life throughout Croatia.

00:14:49.662 --> 00:14:53.642
If you find yourself in such difficulties of life,

00:14:53.642 --> 00:14:59.969
if you are thinking about whether to have an abortion or not – we implore you – don’t do it!

00:14:59.969 --> 00:15:05.854
There are people who care, who will not leave you alone and who will be happy to help you.

00:15:05.854 --> 00:15:07.567
Feel free to contact us.

